  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to estimate the incidence of posttraumatic hypopituitarism, and
      to identify predisposing factors in order to establish a rational responsible socioeconomic
      screening program.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
